narration_text: #C C puts coffee in the mug
#C C picks milk from the fridge
#C C pours milk in the mug
#C C stirs the milk in the mug
#C C picks up bottle of milk
#C C puts milk in the fridge
#C C wipes hand with a napkin
#C C puts mug on the coffee maker
#C C picks up a pack of tea
#C C shakes the pack of tea
#C C puts the pack of coffee in the coffee maker
#C C puts water in the jug
#C C puts the water in the coffee maker
#C C turns on the coffee maker
#C C puts water in the mug
#C C puts the jug kettle heater
#C C pours the dirt in the litter bin
